column5: I hope the Husky made it home to her family!
Heaven forbid people wanting to be treated like people 😐
Funerals are expensive. Who knows what other financial obligations he left behind. Shaming he family because they provided you with free pizza is abhorrent.
Check with vet offices near you. A lot of times they will have adoption boards or centers for people looking for pets and you will know they're going to good homes.
